
To install the InfluxDB router, just use python, there are no other dependencies
If you want to use the ZeroMQ publisher, please ensure that python-zmq is
installed and works.

$ python setup.py build

$ python setup.py install (--prefix)

Configuration file should be in <prefix>/etc and the router can be started with

$ <prefix>/bin/influxdb-router
    Possible options are:
        -h/--help : Help Text
        -c/--config FILE: Configuration file
        -l/--log FILE: Logfile
        -p/--pid FILE: PID file

